Description: Light and fast Polish subtitle downloader from the napi-project
 Napi-bash is bash fork napi.py and expanded with many new features, 
 program is running in cli interface. Assumptions of the simplicity, 
 lightness, speed and minimized requirements. This application 
 download Polish subtitle from the napi-project.
